00:04:45.430 --> 00:04:49.380
Westzynthius, had a method of doing slightly better than this,

00:04:49.810 --> 00:04:54.480
multiply all the numbers up to 100 and then, add two, add three, add five. But it was only slightly better.

00:04:55.600 --> 00:04:57.580
